snippet.title: Cthulhu Realms Digital Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Star Realms has gone insane! Introducing Cthulhu Realms!

Are you zany enough to play the crazier and creepier cousin of Star Realms? In Cthulhu Realms, each player tries to drive their opponent insane or have more sanity than their opponents when the deck runs out.

Download and play today on Android (coming soon on iOS) to find out why Cthulhu Realms is so crazily addictive!
